    <briefdescription>
<para>Decorator that applies median filtering with fixed time base. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Samples the input at regular intervals and applies median filtering to remove spikes and noise. Output updates at the sampling rate.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Motor</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Base motor class (must implement Go(signed short)) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>kWindowSize</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Filter window size (odd number). Default: 5 </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
